    "2) A robust evaluation framework measuring completeness, helpfulness, and factual consistency of code documentation.",
    "3) Comprehensive experiments on diverse repositories show DocAgent consistently outperforms state-of-the-art baselines.",
    "DocAgent operates in two stages to handle complex dependencies and ensure context relevance.",
    "First, the Navigator determines an optimal, dependencyaware processing order (§2.1).",
    "Second, a Multi-Agent System incrementally generates documentation, leveraging specialized agents for code analysis, information retrieval, drafting, and verification (§2.2)."
